  "text": "Gene models were predicted with Augustus v3.2.3 [CITATION_1] using the S. cerevisiae S288C configuration. Gene models were submitted for KEGG annotation using BlastKOALA [CITATION_2] , and GO-terms and functional domains were annotated using InterProScan v5.32-71.0 [CITATION_3] . Orthogroups were assigned with OrthoFinder v2.2.6 [CITATION_4] using representative species from Saccharomycetaceae (Table S4 ) and also using only the haploid Brettanomyces assemblies.",
